(46, 1, '2023-02-27 12:58:19', '2023-02-27 12:58:19', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you would like to know more about me, any projects I am working on or have any comments/questions on my work please contact below:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Phone Number</strong>: <a href=\"tel:07565 646669\">&nbsp;07565 646669</a> <br><strong>Email</strong>: <a href=\"mailto:jordanhickling2000@gmail.com?subject=subject%20text\">jordanhickling2000@gmail.com</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can simply just click on the method text and it will automatically do it for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you would rather make a more specific request (or find if easier) you can use the form below in order to send a request to me!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:wpforms/form-selector {\"formId\":\"89\"} /-->', 'Contact Me', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-me', '', '', '2023-03-01 10:27:25', '2023-03-01 10:27:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=46', 0, 'page', '', 0),
