(52, 1, '2023-02-27 13:04:25', '2023-02-27 13:04:25', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the Gallery of all the images that I have added so far. There could be tons more if there is any images you would like to see then please send a form or contact the team and we will try and get some on there right away for you to browse! Within the gallery you can click on an image to enhance the image. If you find yourself lost on how to close it just click outside of the box and it will automatically click. Why do we have it like this? Well so you can enjoy the images with a closer and with a zoomed in view. So please feel free to browse all the images and enjoy!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now there is not too many images on the Gallery however as the business and website grows we are hoping more and more users will send in their amazing photos so we can add them right here for everyone to see. If you have any photos that you would like to see in this Gallery then please send them my way using my contact information and we will see if its applicable for the Gallery and put it in here! We hope to keep adding thousands of images and make this page the biggest Gallery out there for our users to explore!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some of the upcoming features that we hope to add to this soon are the following:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Filter options - To have an easy way to find the images you want to find using Categories such as \"scenic\", \"Wildlife\", \"Futuristic\" and many more! </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A quicker and more efficient way for users to upload the images themselves with self checks on the images</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>multiple pages - This is just a \"maybe\" feature as depending on how many images there are added we may add multiple gallery pages where you can click arrows and it changes the Gallery (not page per say).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[rl_gallery id=\"55\"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->', 'Image Gallery', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'image-gallery', '', '', '2023-03-09 14:16:25', '2023-03-09 14:16:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=52', 0, 'page', '', 0),
