(166, 1, '2023-03-07 13:14:38', '2023-03-07 13:14:38', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the Gallery of all the images that I have added so far. There could be tons more if there is any images you would like to see then please send a form or contact the team and we will try and get some on there right away for you to browse! Within the gallery you can click on an image to enhance the image. If you find yourself lost on how to close it just click outside of the box and it will automatically click. Why do we have it like this? Well so you can enjoy the images with a closer and with a zoomed in view. So please feel free to browse all the images and enjoy!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[rl_gallery id=\"55\"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->', 'Image Gallery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '52-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-07 13:14:38', '2023-03-07 13:14:38', '', 52, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=166', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(168, 1, '2023-03-07 13:20:59', '2023-03-07 13:20:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before you leave this page I thought I would quickly tell you how to get back here when you need/want to. You see there is not a \"Homepage\" tab on the menu and that maybe confusing. However I made it this way because it makes the navigation menu look a lot better. All you need to do to get back here is click the \"WordPress Reflection\" title right above this page\'s title. That will then send you to this page. If you wish to not use the menu at the top and would rather find your way around on this page instead I will include (hopefully) a list of all the pages that you can get too so it\'s all here for your convenience. Hope you enjoy my website! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Who is \"Pictures For You\"?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently it is just a single person making the website someone who can put in images when requested and someone who is enthusiastic about building a website for photography lovers. The company is just a small made up company but if there was some sort of build up on this I would imagine having ways of uploading users photo\'s through emails or even through a simple \"upload file\" button. People can share there own images like in Instagram but have a collection within a gallery. Constantly upping the experience and the website with WordPress to keep getting better with the tool and making even more websites along with it. Of course, we wouldn\'t let all of the users do all the picture taking themselves we would have some professionals in the team ourselves and capture some of the most amazing pictures around the world!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>What can you find on this website?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This website is designed for any photographer out there that wants to upload images to a gallery that will display it in a lightbox. This website is used to just upload some nice images onto a simple webpage. These photos can be categorized as anything the whole plan for this website is to just have a whole bunch of images all in one place so users can just scroll through them all. You will also have latest posts about any news in the photography industry where you can read up on your favourite articles and learn more about the field.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Homepage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '113-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-07 13:20:59', '2023-03-07 13:20:59', '', 113, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=168', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(169, 1, '2023-03-07 13:22:10', '2023-03-07 13:22:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A website filled with all of your favourite pictures!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Who is \"Pictures For You\"?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently it is just a single person making the website someone who can put in images when requested and someone who is enthusiastic about building a website for photography lovers. The company is just a small made up company but if there was some sort of build up on this I would imagine having ways of uploading users photo\'s through emails or even through a simple \"upload file\" button. People can share there own images like in Instagram but have a collection within a gallery. Constantly upping the experience and the website with WordPress to keep getting better with the tool and making even more websites along with it. Of course, we wouldn\'t let all of the users do all the picture taking themselves we would have some professionals in the team ourselves and capture some of the most amazing pictures around the world!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>What can you find on this website?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This website is designed for any photographer out there that wants to upload images to a gallery that will display it in a lightbox. This website is used to just upload some nice images onto a simple webpage. These photos can be categorized as anything the whole plan for this website is to just have a whole bunch of images all in one place so users can just scroll through them all. You will also have latest posts about any news in the photography industry where you can read up on your favourite articles and learn more about the field.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pictures For You', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '113-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-07 13:22:10', '2023-03-07 13:22:10', '', 113, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=169', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
