(178, 1, '2023-03-09 14:07:14', '2023-03-09 14:07:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hello! My name is Jordan I made this WordPress website alone.. Well with some help of some plugins too of course! I am a trainee web developer branching towards Junior Web Development roles and have used multiple languages which I will list below with the projects of each of them languages. I thoroughly enjoy coding as tough as it but the reward at the end to see a product you made work is always the best feeling. I am currently on a Website Development Scion Scheme for Netmatters learning how to code in multiple languages that\'s how most of these products have been made.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>So what other coding languages have I used?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As this is my first time making a WordPress website I would like to try and put as much information that I can on it and this is actually one that I feel like could actually be used pretty strongly. The reason why is because the results of each website actually reflect on what the programming language is being used. For example I have a JavaScript Array website which is mainly just used to grab an image and assign it to an email. Because of that a lot of focus went into the design for a simple page for them array\'s meanwhile one that focuses on making a Portfolio focused a lot more on the layout and design, so sharing all these project may spark some interest. Along with the project description I will also provide a link to the website which will open in a new tab!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://jordan-hickling.netmatters-scs.co.uk/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://jordan-hickling.netmatters-scs.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">Portfolio</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":131,\"width\":556,\"height\":287,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/portfolio-1024x528.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-131\" width=\"556\" height=\"287\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong><em>My Portfolio\'s Homepage</em></strong></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My portfolio project is a project that nearly any website developer needs it\'s used to show off the projects (kind of like how I am doing here but in a much more professional manor) and to describe yourself and the projects themselves. This hosts a lot of information that I have on here but has my whole design and a lot more freedom with the HTML!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://netmatters.jordan-hickling.netmatters-scs.co.uk/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://netmatters.jordan-hickling.netmatters-scs.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">Netmatters Replica Website</a></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":134,\"width\":552,\"height\":267,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/netmatters-replica-1024x497.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-134\" width=\"552\" height=\"267\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em><strong>My Netmatters Page replica</strong></em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This website was the first website that I built this was a test on how well I know HTML and CSS and how much I can replica a website from the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.netmatters.co.uk/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.netmatters.co.uk/\" target=