(202, 1, '2023-03-08 11:28:03', '2023-03-08 11:28:03', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A website filled with all of your favourite pictures!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Who is \"Pictures For You\"?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently it is just a single person making the website someone who can put in images when requested and someone who is enthusiastic about building a website for photography lovers. The company is just a small made up company but if there was some sort of build up on this I would imagine having ways of uploading users photo\'s through emails or even through a simple \"upload file\" button. People can share there own images like in Instagram but have a collection within a gallery. Constantly upping the experience and the website with WordPress to keep getting better with the tool and making even more websites along with it. Of course, we wouldn\'t let all of the users do all the picture taking themselves we would have some professionals in the team ourselves and capture some of the most amazing pictures around the world!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>What can you find on this website?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This website is designed for any photographer out there that wants to upload images to a gallery that will display it in a lightbox. This website is used to just upload some nice images onto a simple webpage. These photos can be categorized as anything the whole plan for this website is to just have a whole bunch of images all in one place so users can just scroll through them all. You will also have latest posts about any news in the photography industry where you can read up on your favourite articles and learn more about the field.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":107,\"width\":-2